gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 114, Bucks 106
gameRecap.excerpt: Phoenix defeats Milwaukee, 114-106. For Phoenix, Devin Booker led the way with 32 points and four assists while Kevin Durant added 28 points and 10 rebounds. Giannis Antetokounmpo led the way with 34 points, 10 rebounds, and six assists for Milwaukee in the losing effort. Phoenix wins and improves to 30-21, while Milwaukee moves to 33-18 in the loss.
